## List of [Registered Historic Places](/National_Register_of_Historic_Places) in [Clark County, Nevada](/Clark_County,_Nevada), USA

The locations of [National Register](/National_Register_of_Historic_Places) properties and districts, particularly those showing latitude and longitude coordinates, can be pinpointed on an interactive map. Just click "Map of all coordinates." It’s a digital breadcrumb trail for the historically inclined, or perhaps just the lost. &#91;1&#93;

